data.description: DON'T MISS OUT!! This is an excellent opportunity to own a spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom split level home located in the Village of Frankfort. This home has great upside once the property has been updated and has a great backyard for entertaining. The property is located near schools, train station, parks, and retail. The pictures of the rooms have been virtually renovated to show buyers a vision of a finished product. A must see!!
